    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Самолетики над городом]]></title>
    <link href="http://ryabko.github.io/octopress/blog/2011/09/08/samolietiki-nad-ghorodom/"/>
    <updated>2011-09-08T00:34:00+04:00</updated>
